title: The Blacklist (OST)
description:
This is not actually the Blacklist OST but I couldn't find a download of it anywhere so I downloaded a load of the tracks used in the series and put it together in a torrent.

Probably haven't got all of them and they may have varying quality but I just thought I'd share with others who may want them but don't want to have to go searching for each track individually or until someone posts a better version.
